<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta name="description" content="Personal website for Cristiano Silva Jr.">
        <title>Hello!</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/purecss@0.6.2/build/pure-min.css" integrity="sha384-" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/purecss@0.6.2/build/grids-responsive-min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.css">
        <style>
            {{.Style}}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="header">
            <div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
                <a class="pure-menu-heading" href="/"><i class="fa fa-smile-o"></i>
					Cris Silva Jr.
				</a>

                <!-- <ul class="pure-menu-list">
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Experiences</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Downloads</a></li>
                </ul> -->
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="splash-container">
            <div class="splash">
                <h1 class="splash-head">Cris Silva Jr.</h1>
                <p class="splash-subhead">
                    I turn coffee and donuts into solutions to problems.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="content">
                <h2 class="content-head is-center">What can I offer you?</h2>

                <div class="pure-g">
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">

                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-bolt"></i>
                            Control &amp; Automation Engineering
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            I work with Digital Signal Procesing, and most of my experiences revolved around producing dedicated software tools for analysing biomedical signals and the documentation for these applications.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-sitemap"></i>
                            Project Manager
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            I organize teams and workspaces towards a common goal using modern time and project management tools.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ribbon l-box-lrg pure-g">
                <h2 class="content-head content-head-ribbon">What have I already built?</h2>

                <div class="pure-g">
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-file"></i>
                            <a class="joe-ribbon-header" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/edf">EDF+ Implementation</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p>An <a class="joe-ribbon" href="http://www.edfplus.info/">EDF+</a> implementation for Go.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
                            <a class="joe-ribbon-header" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/Counter/releases">Counting Sheep</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p>An Android app to count. Simple as that. <a class="joe-ribbon" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/Counter">Source code available.</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-list-ul"></i>
                            <a class="joe-ribbon-header" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/failproof/releases">Failproof Checklists</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p>A place for your checklists. Everyone has got their own after all. <a class="joe-ribbon" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/failproof-api">Source code available.</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-dollar"></i>
                            <a class="joe-ribbon-header" href="http://logey.herokuapp.com">Logey</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p>An online money logging tool. <a class="joe-ribbon" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/moneyweb">Source code available.</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h2 class="content-head is-center">How can you find me?</h2>

                <div class="pure-g">
                    <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
                        <h4>Send me an e-mail!</h4>
                        <p>
                            My e-mail is <a class="joe-link" href="mailto:cristianoalvesjr@gmail.com">cristianoalvesjr@gmail.com</a>
                        </p>

                        <h4>More Information...</h4>
                        <p>
                            You can find me at <a class="joe-link" href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu">GitHub</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            {{.Script}}
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
